               <msContents>

                  <summary>Excerpt from the Missal, prayer of thanksgiving; Image of the Sufferings; Hymn to Christ "O Christ the Stranger"; Congregation of the Faithful; Mystagogia; Wisest of the Wise; Prayer, “For the sake of the peaceful holy things,”; Prayer Against the Tongue of People; Lament of the Soul; Image of the Trinity; Image of Gäbrä Mänfas Qǝddus; Hymn to Gäbrä Mänfas Qǝddus, “Greeting to you, Gäbrä Mänfas Qǝddus, the Righteous,”; Image of Gabriel; Image of the Miracles of Ewosṭatewos;Image of Ewosṭatewos; Image of the Four Creatures; Image of Mary; Image of the Covenant of Mercy; Image of Mary of Qʷǝsqʷam; Hymn to Mary, “The sound of your cry, Mary, echos in my consciousness,”; Image of the Icon; Image of Mary of Edom; Hymn to Mary, “Rejoice, Mary, virgin in body and mind; Image of Joachim and Anna; Hymn to Anna, Mother of Mary, “Greeting to you, sweet of memory and name,”; Image of Arägawi Zä-Mika’el; Hymn to Aragawi, “Rock of the Gospel; Image of Garima; Hymn to Garima, “Blessedness for you, Garima,”; Image of Täklä Haymanot; Hymn to Täklä Haymanot, “Greeting to you, Your Peace Discovers Us; Image of Ewosṭatewos; Image of Samuel; Image of Afqäränä Ǝgzi’; Hymn to Afqäränä Ǝgzi’, “Greeting to you, Afqäränä Ǝgzi’, Pillar of the Church”; Image of Minas; Hymn to Minas, “Greeting to you, Minas, the Chosen,”; Canticle of the Flower; Image of Mary; Excerpt from the image of the Christian Sabbath [Sunday]</summary>

